entry.title: What is wrong with me?
entry.content:
Another ranting, because none is listening, or do I have none?

It seems the last question is the point. Somehow that’s my feeling.

But it doesn’t matter here, I just hate this headache that attacks me again in the last 3 days. No, I don’t want you to care, I just want to make myself feeling better by writing this.

And if it helps, I’ll do, I will do all to make myself feeling better, because none just does it.

But it’s okay, totally okay.
